//			  the case of RTL scripts like Hebrew and Arabic
//			* after: places tooltip to the right of the target node/widget, or to the left in
//			  the case of RTL scripts like Hebrew and Arabic
//			* above: tooltip goes above target node
//			* below: tooltip goes below target node
//
